This project demonstrates the following features:

	* Determining whether or not a device is plugged in
	* Receiving notifications when the power state changes
	* Enabling/disabling the Auto-Lock based upon the power state
	
The project contains a Settings bundle to allow the user to dictate the behavior of the 
application when it is plugged in.

If you have any questions about this source code, you can contact me in the following ways:

* Twitter: neilco
* Email: neilco@gmail.com
* iChat: neilcowburn

You are free to use this source code in both commercial and non-commercial applications. 

This source code is to accompany the blog post at the URL below:

http://www.neilcowburn.com/2009/07/28/disable-auto-lock-on-the-iphone-when-plugged-in

